    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157220/extras/5c5a8fb3282231bce8223518318d18bd.avif?t=1726239555\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br>Cozy Desktop is an application that helps you relax and create a nice, comforting cozy vibe while you use your computer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weather Effects</h2>You can have various global weather effects that play on your computer no matter what you're doing. Whether it's playing a game, writing a paper, coding, or listening to music, you can play these weather effects to set the right mood. All weather effects are customizable, allowing you to adjust properties such as <strong>intensity</strong>, <strong>volume </strong>and other visual elements. Effects include Rain, Snow, Falling Leaves and a camp fire.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard/Mouse sounds</h2>Choose from a variety of sounds to add to each mouse click or key press. (With adjustable volume)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Companions</h2>Summon friendly companions that motivate you and hang out in the corner (can be disabled or moved to a different location). Catch and unlock new companions as they spawn every once in a while!",
